## ⚙️ Tech Stack (Finalized)

### Architecture: **Flutter (UI) + Unity 3D (Game) + Supabase (Backend)**

A hybrid approach where **Flutter handles all 11 UI screens** (premium glassmorphism, smooth animations) and **Unity handles the full 3D city world** (skyline rendering, cruise/helicopter mode). Connected via `flutter_unity_widget`.

### Source of Truth Policy (Implementation)

- **Final architecture is locked for v1**: Flutter + Unity 3D + Supabase backend
- **Supporting services are part of this final stack**: Firebase Auth + FCM, Upstash Redis, Health Connect
- If two docs conflict, **the latest approved update is the source of truth**
- If implementation reveals a bug/constraint, we update docs + decision log, and the **new latest approved update becomes truth**

| Layer | Technology | Why |
|---|---|---|
| **App UI (11 screens)** | **Flutter (Dart)** | Best-in-class glassmorphism, smooth transitions, cross-platform, hot reload |
| **3D Game (2 screens)** | **Unity 3D (C#) + URP** | Full 3D rendering, custom shaders, Cinemachine camera, procedural buildings |
| **Auth** | **Firebase Auth** | Google Sign-In, JWT tokens, best Flutter SDK |
| **Database** | **Supabase (PostgreSQL)** | Real SQL (JOINs, window functions for leaderboards), RLS, Realtime, easy migration |
| **Server Logic** | **Supabase Edge Functions (TypeScript)** | Task completion validation, anti-cheat, streak recovery, atomic transactions |
| **Leaderboards + Cache** | **Upstash Redis** | Sorted sets for O(1) rank queries, atomic raid boss counters, rate limiting |
| **Push Notifications** | **Firebase Cloud Messaging** | Streak warnings, health reports |
| **File Storage** | **Supabase Storage** | Avatars, screenshots |
| **Scheduled Jobs** | **pg_cron (Supabase)** | Midnight streak check, grace day reset, mayor rotation |
| **Health Data** | **Google Health Connect** | Steps, running, cycling auto-sync |

**Architecture diagram:**
```
┌──────────────────────────────────────┐
│         Flutter (Dart) — 11 Screens  │
│  Glassmorphism UI · Space Grotesk    │
│  Dark theme · Smooth transitions     │
├──────────────────────────────────────┤
│  flutter_unity_widget bridge ↕       │
├──────────────────────────────────────┤
│    Unity 3D (C#) — 2 Screens        │
│  Full 3D cyberpunk city · URP       │
│  Cruise/Helicopter · Custom shaders  │
├──────────────────────────────────────┤
│         ↕ Health Connect API         │
├──────────────────────────────────────┤
│       Supabase (PostgreSQL)          │
│  REST API · Realtime · Edge Fns     │
│  + Upstash Redis (leaderboards)     │
├──────────────────────────────────────┤
│       Firebase Auth + FCM            │
└──────────────────────────────────────┘
```

> [!NOTE]
> **Migration-safe**: Supabase IS PostgreSQL. If you outgrow Supabase at scale, migration to self-hosted Postgres (AWS RDS/GCP Cloud SQL) is a standard `pg_dump` → `pg_restore` — zero query rewrites needed.

